channel.title: New release of a sample pack mean a new remix
channel.description: I have been thinking how can the auxy team be more active in the community of challenges, so each time there is a new sample pack release a thread is created to remix it and the person who host/the thread will judge the songs and auxy maybe able to shout them out for a prize. Just a thought nothing more.
